WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:01:10.880 --> 00:01:11.640
Time's up.

00:01:21.640 --> 00:01:22.570
We have a signal.

00:01:27.120 --> 00:01:27.800
Why?

00:01:28.800 --> 00:01:30.330
Why are there so many places

00:01:30.400 --> 00:01:31.680
transmitting at the same time?

00:01:31.680 --> 00:01:32.440
Could it be

00:01:32.640 --> 00:01:34.160
that they added more manpower

00:01:34.160 --> 00:01:35.840
and are transmitting from multiple locations simultaneously?

00:01:35.840 --> 00:01:36.520
Idiots.

00:01:36.680 --> 00:01:37.840
The bands are all the same.

00:01:37.840 --> 00:01:39.720
Transmitting and receiving at the same time

00:01:39.720 --> 00:01:41.080
means everything will be messed up on the other end.

00:01:41.080 --> 00:01:42.539
Then what should we do now?

00:01:43.039 --> 00:01:44.320
There must be a mole.

00:01:44.920 --> 00:01:46.960
I must find the real signal.

00:02:27.480 --> 00:02:28.680
Thirty seconds left.

00:03:00.320 --> 00:03:01.450
Done transmitting.

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:26.040
Don't move!

00:03:33.120 --> 00:03:34.180
Where is the radio?

00:03:36.520 --> 00:03:37.160
Search!

00:03:41.400 --> 00:03:42.400
The radio is here.

00:03:56.480 --> 00:03:57.360
It's not a radio.

00:03:57.360 --> 00:03:58.720
It's a high-frequency jammer.

00:03:58.720 --> 00:03:59.780
We've been fooled.

00:04:02.800 --> 00:04:03.920
Not again.

00:04:05.600 --> 00:04:07.260
Our air-ground coordination

00:04:08.480 --> 00:04:09.680
is like a joke.

00:04:10.240 --> 00:04:11.970
The jammer has been destroyed,

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:13.160
but they

00:04:13.520 --> 00:04:15.400
still successfully transmitted.

00:04:15.400 --> 00:04:16.200
Transmitted.

00:04:16.240 --> 00:04:17.600
It's my dereliction of duty.

00:04:17.600 --> 00:04:19.880
I failed to predict the underground party's actions in advance.

00:04:19.880 --> 00:04:21.079
Dereliction of duty?

00:04:22.480 --> 00:04:24.280
Is saying 'dereliction of duty' enough?

00:04:24.280 --> 00:04:25.360
The empire's face

00:04:25.720 --> 00:04:27.520
has been completely lost by you!

00:04:29.920 --> 00:04:30.600
Captain,

00:04:31.040 --> 00:04:32.040
in my opinion,

00:04:32.600 --> 00:04:33.880
those underground party members,

00:04:33.880 --> 00:04:36.540
they won't shed tears until they see the coffin.

00:04:36.640 --> 00:04:37.560
Don't we have

00:04:37.720 --> 00:04:40.380
a group of anti-Japanese elements in our hands?

00:04:43.680 --> 00:04:44.610
What do you mean?

00:04:46.520 --> 00:04:47.480
Kill a batch,

00:04:47.920 --> 00:04:49.400
show them some color,

00:04:49.720 --> 00:04:50.640
let them know

00:04:51.080 --> 00:04:52.400
that opposing the empire

00:04:52.400 --> 00:04:53.800
is a dead end.

00:05:07.520 --> 00:05:08.520
Where is the list?

00:05:08.920 --> 00:05:10.080
I'll draw it up right away.

00:05:10.080 --> 00:05:11.520
Oh right, there's one person

00:05:11.520 --> 00:05:12.580
who must be killed.

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:13.760
Who is it?

00:05:14.440 --> 00:05:15.280
Gu Xiaoxiong.

00:05:16.640 --> 00:05:17.880
Gu Xiaoxiong?

00:05:18.880 --> 00:05:19.920
You mean

00:05:20.320 --> 00:05:21.840
the captain of the harmonica team?

00:05:21.840 --> 00:05:22.480
Yes.

00:05:22.840 --> 00:05:25.440
He is a die-hard anti-Japanese element.

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:27.880
He's the most stubborn person

00:05:28.120 --> 00:05:29.240
I've encountered during interrogations.

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:31.400
Killing him taking this opportunity

00:05:31.960 --> 00:05:33.159
can also deter those

00:05:33.280 --> 00:05:34.640
who are wavering.

00:05:37.320 --> 00:05:39.120
Draw up the execution list immediately.

00:05:39.120 --> 00:05:40.040
First thing tomorrow morning,

00:05:40.040 --> 00:05:41.840
post the notices on the streets.

00:05:41.920 --> 00:05:44.280
Yes, we'll arrange it right away.

00:05:54.480 --> 00:05:56.880
I didn't expect the enemy to strike so fast.

00:05:58.000 --> 00:06:00.060
We must quickly find a way to save him.

00:06:05.440 --> 00:06:06.160
I,

00:06:06.760 --> 00:06:07.560
Zhan Li,

00:06:08.120 --> 00:06:08.840
A Jin,

00:06:09.760 --> 00:06:10.760
have three guns.

00:06:11.040 --> 00:06:11.880
If brother...

00:06:12.560 --> 00:06:13.960
Force definitely won't work.

00:06:13.960 --> 00:06:15.240
The Secret Service Section is heavily guarded.

00:06:15.240 --> 00:06:17.370
Using force is just a suicide mission.

00:06:22.040 --> 00:06:23.170
I'll go see Matsuda.

00:06:35.800 --> 00:06:36.460
Reporting.

00:06:36.880 --> 00:06:37.720
Captain Matsuda.

00:06:37.720 --> 00:06:38.800
The guests have arrived.

00:06:38.800 --> 00:06:39.480
Come in.

00:06:45.400 --> 00:06:46.520
Captain Matsuda.

00:06:47.159 --> 00:06:48.760
Sorry to interrupt your work.

00:06:48.760 --> 00:06:49.560
Not at all.

00:06:49.800 --> 00:06:51.680
I heard Mr. Schiele was coming.

00:06:51.880 --> 00:06:54.080
I've been waiting here for a long time.

00:06:55.159 --> 00:06:55.880
Please sit.

00:07:01.240 --> 00:07:02.840
Miss Qin, please have a seat.

00:07:08.360 --> 00:07:11.160
This is a gift Miss Qin prepared for you.

00:07:11.400 --> 00:07:13.000
Liao Dynasty ceramics.

00:07:13.120 --> 00:07:14.980
I heard when you were in Fengtian,

00:07:15.040 --> 00:07:16.700
you particularly liked this.

00:07:21.160 --> 00:07:23.600
I remember telling Miss Qin

00:07:24.920 --> 00:07:26.200
that I've washed my hands

00:07:26.200 --> 00:07:27.600
of the antique business.

00:07:28.720 --> 00:07:29.720
Mr. Matsuda.

00:07:30.560 --> 00:07:33.240
This is a small token of appreciation from Mr. Schiele and me.

00:07:33.240 --> 00:07:35.040
It's also a show of my sincerity.

00:07:38.159 --> 00:07:40.320
This gift is too valuable.

00:07:40.800 --> 00:07:41.800
I can't accept it.

00:07:47.600 --> 00:07:48.520
What is that?

00:07:49.080 --> 00:07:52.520
This is from the Hohner harmonica factory in Germany.

00:07:52.520 --> 00:07:54.200
It's a newly released harmonica.

00:07:54.200 --> 00:07:56.720
I thought maybe you'd like it.

00:08:07.600 --> 00:08:08.720
Mr. Schiele.

00:08:09.000 --> 00:08:10.680
That's very thoughtful of you.

00:08:10.680 --> 00:08:11.760
Captain Matsuda.

00:08:12.240 --> 00:08:16.120
Actually, I came today to ask you for a favor.

00:08:18.000 --> 00:08:19.800
It's about Gu Xiaoxiong, right?

00:08:22.200 --> 00:08:23.240
Mr. Matsuda.

00:08:24.880 --> 00:08:26.880
I went back and thought about it last time.

00:08:26.880 --> 00:08:28.920
Regarding Mr. Schiele's and my harmonica club,

00:08:28.920 --> 00:08:30.380
it was my poor management.

00:08:30.800 --> 00:08:31.720
It was my fault.

00:08:31.960 --> 00:08:34.120
But then again,

00:08:34.400 --> 00:08:36.960
he shouldn't be shot directly.

00:08:37.559 --> 00:08:38.880
He is just a child.

00:08:39.200 --> 00:08:39.880
Yes.

00:08:40.360 --> 00:08:42.220
Gu Xiaoxiong is indeed stubborn.

00:08:42.440 --> 00:08:43.440
Mr. Matsuda.

00:08:43.880 --> 00:08:45.560
Mr. Schiele and I promise you,

00:08:45.800 --> 00:08:47.480
once he returns to the harmonica club,

00:08:47.480 --> 00:08:48.800
he will absolutely not do

00:08:48.800 --> 00:08:50.730
anything against the rules again.

00:08:55.640 --> 00:08:58.120
Miss Qin is my capable assistant.

00:08:58.560 --> 00:09:01.240
She helps me manage the business in Harbin

00:09:01.720 --> 00:09:03.120
and does quite well.

00:09:03.240 --> 00:09:05.920
Moreover, she is the daughter of your old friend.

00:09:05.920 --> 00:09:07.380
There is a saying in China,

00:09:07.720 --> 00:09:09.180
if not for the monk's sake,

00:09:09.920 --> 00:09:11.180
then for the Buddha's.

00:09:11.520 --> 00:09:12.480
Mr. Matsuda.

00:09:14.840 --> 00:09:16.240
Just let Gu Xiaoxiong go.

00:09:16.640 --> 00:09:17.700
Even if it's just to

00:09:17.800 --> 00:09:19.280
do Mr. Schiele a favor.

00:09:28.960 --> 00:09:29.640
Alright.

00:09:32.040 --> 00:09:32.960
I'll do

00:09:33.160 --> 00:09:34.490
Mr. Schiele this favor.

00:09:36.200 --> 00:09:37.460
As long as Gu Xiaoxiong

00:09:37.640 --> 00:09:39.360
signs the repentance letter

00:09:39.560 --> 00:09:40.960
and leaves his fingerprint,

00:09:40.960 --> 00:09:41.890
I will let him go.

00:09:42.000 --> 00:09:43.360
No problem.

00:09:43.440 --> 00:09:44.160
I guarantee

00:09:44.240 --> 00:09:45.770
he will definitely sign it.

00:09:46.720 --> 00:09:47.600
Miss Qin.

00:09:48.240 --> 00:09:49.120
Do you think

00:09:49.480 --> 00:09:50.440
he will sign it?

00:09:53.720 --> 00:09:54.520
Someone come.

00:09:57.320 --> 00:09:59.600
Have Gu Xiaoxiong sign a repentance letter

00:09:59.600 --> 00:10:01.040
and bring it here immediately.

00:10:01.040 --> 00:10:01.760
Yes, sir.

00:10:12.760 --> 00:10:13.520
Wake up.

00:10:18.120 --> 00:10:19.040
Miss Qin

00:10:19.360 --> 00:10:20.620
wants you to sign this.

00:10:21.480 --> 00:10:22.880
You're only 24 years old.

00:10:23.840 --> 00:10:24.680
Surviving

00:10:25.120 --> 00:10:26.980
is more important than anything.

00:10:27.080 --> 00:10:28.080
Only by surviving

00:10:28.600 --> 00:10:29.860
can life have meaning.

00:10:32.880 --> 00:10:36.140
Have you ever seen the Erman's birch on Changbai Mountain?

00:10:37.560 --> 00:10:39.220
Even when cracked by the cold,

00:10:39.920 --> 00:10:41.720
they still grow towards the sky.

00:10:45.800 --> 00:10:47.400
Sometimes dying

00:10:49.000 --> 00:10:50.800
is more meaningful than living.

00:10:54.240 --> 00:10:55.570
You are truly stubborn.

00:11:25.680 --> 00:11:26.720
I know what to do.

00:11:28.880 --> 00:11:30.080
I won't say anything.

00:11:30.160 --> 00:11:31.360
I didn't see anything.

00:11:31.360 --> 00:11:32.620
I don't know anything.

00:11:38.560 --> 00:11:39.690
They should be here.

00:11:45.040 --> 00:11:45.800
It's them.

00:11:51.320 --> 00:11:52.320
Come, Xiaoxiong.

00:11:52.680 --> 00:11:53.600
Slow down.

00:14:07.120 --> 00:14:08.000
Ms. Qin.

00:14:10.680 --> 00:14:12.880
But I can't play the harmonica anymore.

00:14:19.960 --> 00:14:20.720
Xiaoxiong.

00:14:21.640 --> 00:14:22.480
Don't worry.

00:14:23.720 --> 00:14:25.180
I will find all of Harbin's

00:14:25.320 --> 00:14:27.120
best doctors to treat your hand.

00:14:27.280 --> 00:14:28.080
In the future,

00:14:28.920 --> 00:14:31.520
you can still play the harmonica for everyone.

00:14:37.400 --> 00:14:38.680
Where is my harmonica?

00:14:52.440 --> 00:14:53.200
Xiaoxiong.

00:14:54.280 --> 00:14:55.040
Xiaoxiong.

00:14:56.160 --> 00:14:57.080
What's wrong?

00:14:57.760 --> 00:14:58.520
Xiaoxiong.